scripts are called in alphabetic order (echo $dir/* to check the order)
sysinit   - scripts in here are called before anything else
boot      - scripts in here are alled after sysinit
default   - scripts in here are called after boot
post      - scripts in here are the last scripts to be called during boot

powerdown - scripts in here are called before poweroff / reboot
poweroff  - called at poweroff
reboot    - called at reboot
